FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://downing.club/

# Music-Mecca API

Music Mecca is a source for information about musicians and bands, as well as the music they release.

# Group Artists

Artists are all musicians stored in our database. That includes solo artists or bands.

## Artist [/artists/{artistId}]

