# Group Songs

Songs are any pieces of music the artist has created.

## Song [/songs/{songId}]

+ Model (application/json)
            + Headers
              Location: http://downing.club/songs/2

    + Body

            {
                "id": 2,
                "name": "Eminem",
                "lyrics": "blah blah blah",
                "uri": "/songs/2",
                "audioUrl": "www.youtube.com/blahblahblah",
                "video": {
                    "id": 1,
                    "name": "Fack Video",
                    "year": "2003"
                }
            }

### Get a Song [GET]
+ Parameters
    + songId (id) - ID of the Song

+ Response 200
[Song][]

